      "date": "2025-01-16 02:05:48.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nPatch 57717 is actually fixing a number of test cases, but doesn't quite fix all of them:\n\n /usr/share/pjdfstest/chown/00.t .. \n not ok 312 - tried '-u 65532 -g 65531 -- chown pjdfstest_0a7af -1 -1',\n    expected 0, got EPERM\n not ok 319 - tried '-u 65532 -g 65531 -- chown pjdfstest_0a7af[e -1 -1',\n    expected 0, got EPERM\n not ok 327 - tried '-u 65532 -g 65531 -- lchown pjdfstest_0a7af -1 -1',\n    expected 0, got EPERM\n\nThe following test cases were previously failing and are fixed by patch 57717:\n\n not ok 641 - tried '-u 65534 -g 65533,65532 chown pjdfstest_03db8 65534 65532',\n    expected 0, got EACCES\n not ok 642 - tried 'stat pjdfstest_03db8 mode,uid,gid',\n    expected 0555,65534,65532, got 06555,65534,65533\n not ok 644 - tried 'stat pjdfstest_03db8 mode,uid,gid',\n    expected 06555,65534,65532, got 06555,65534,65533\n not ok 656 - tried '-u 65534 -g 65533,65532 chown pjdfstest_f12ba8 65534 65532',\n    expected 0, got EACCES\n not ok 657 - tried 'stat pjdfstest_03db8 mode,uid,gid',\n    expected 0555,65534,65532, got 06555,65534,65533\n not ok 658 - tried 'stat pjdfstest_f12ba mode,uid,gid',\n    expected 0555,65534,65532, got 06555,65534,65533\n not ok 660 - tried 'stat pjdfstest_03db8 mode,uid,gid', \n    expected 06555,65534,65532, got 06555,65534,65533\n not ok 661 - tried 'stat pjdfstest_f12ba mode,uid,gid',\n    expected 06555,65534,65532, got 06555,65534,65533\n not ok 677 - tried '-u 65534 -g 65533,65532 lchown pjdfstest_03db8 65534 65532',\n    expected 0, got EACCES\n not ok 678 - tried 'lstat pjdfstest_03db8 mode,uid,gid',\n    expected 0555,65534,65532, got 06555,65534,65533\n not ok 680 - tried 'lstat pjdfstest_03db8 mode,uid,gid',\n    expected 06555,65534,65532, got 06555,65534,65533",
